      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, so it runs like a dream. It's super comfy and perfect for both daily commutes and weekend road trips. Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it feels on the road!",
